snippet.title: Rita Moreno Dated Elvis Presley To Get Revenge On Cheating Marlon Brando
snippet.description:
Rita Moreno joined the ladies of "The View" and revealed she dated Elvis Presley to get revenge on her cheating ex Marlon Brando but recalls Elvis being "sweet but boring.” Morgan Hoffman and Carlos Bustamante react on ET Canada Live.

#RitaMoreno #MarlonBrando #ElvisPresley
